md:
giải nghĩa từ "beauties" sang tiếng việt; đưa ra nghĩa tiếng việt theo từ loại và đưa ra câu ví dụ, các từ liên quan.

* Beauties: (noun) plural of beauty
	+ Meaning: Things or people that are pleasing to the eye or mind.
	+ Example sentence: The beauties of nature are on full display in this national park.
	+ Related words: beauty, beautiful, beautifully, beautify

Note: The word "beauties" is a plural noun, meaning it refers to multiple things or people that are pleasing to the eye or mind.
